about_eminent_desc.description: At Eminent Interior Design in Minneapolis, MN, we focus on putting our clients’ ideas first. Your kitchen, bathroom, or overall interior design is about your everyday life and passions, this foundational understanding makes working with our team easy, rewarding and fun. In the end, we want their homes to reflect them, not only their designer’s influence.

authors.about: Brandi’s interior design portfolio includes a vast array of projects from sleek contemporary condos to formal traditional homes. Her current focus includes new construction, interior design and remodeling project collaborations with many Twin Cities’ top builders and architects. She is an award-winning interior designer based in Minneapolis, MN with more than 20 years of industry experience. Explore her portfolio.

We’re thrilled Katie accepted the Senior Designer role here at Eminent. She brings with her an impressive project portfolio and a spunky personality everyone loves. Katie loves living in the city in the St Anthony Historic area of Minneapolis. After graduating from Mankato State with a BS in interior design and construction management, she worked at several firms before joining Eminent. During her free time Katie enjoys dancing and spending time at her family’s Two Harbors lake house.
